These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-1::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  chef, manager
The people use 2 different means of transport: subway, trike
1. the chef is on the left of the person driving the subway##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Job   | chef  | manager |
| Transport     | trike | subway  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-2::.
There 2 different types of food: eggplant, kiwi
The people have 2 different hobbies: gardening, chess
1. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2       |
| Food    | eggplant      | kiwi         |
| Hobby   | gardening | chess |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-3::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  electrician, police-officer
There 2 different types of food: orange, spinach
1. the electrician is on the right of the person eating spinach##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |
| Job   | police-officer | electrician   |
| Food       | spinach  | orange |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-4::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, fonseca
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: cycling, parkour
1. the fonseca-smoker is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |
| Cigar   | montecristo  | fonseca |
| Sport         | cycling | parkour    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-5::.
2 different pets are kept: pony, goat
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: crime, horror
1. the owner of the pony is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |   2    |
| Pet      | pony | goat |
| Movie-Genre   | horror        | crime  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-6::.
There are 2 different nationalities: colombian, thai
